nter\">5 gp</td></tr><tr><th></th><th></th><th></th><th></th><th></th><th></th><th></th><th></th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"8\"><em><strong>Notes: </strong></em>A successful hit means the target is <strong>@Compendium[sweb-core-rules.savage-eberron-rules.Bound and Entangled]{Entangled}</strong>. The net is @Compendium[sweb-core-rules.savage-eberron-rules.Breaking Things]{Hardness} 10 and vulnerable only to cutting attacks.</td></tr></tbody></table><p></p><table><tbody><tr><th class=\"main-heading\" colspan=\"4\">Ranged weapons ammunition</th></tr><tr><th class=\"sub-heading left\">Ammunition</th><th class=\"sub-heading\">Cost</th><th class=\"sub-heading\">Weight</th><th class=\"sub-heading left\">Notes</th></tr><tr><td>@Compendium[sweb-core-rules.savage-eberron-gear.Arrow]{Arrow}</td><td style=\"text-align:center\">1 gp/20</td><td style=\"text-align:center\">3 lbs/20</td><td style=\"text-align:left\">—</td></tr><tr><td>@Compendium[sweb-core-rules.savage-eberron-gear.Arrow, Alchemist's Acid]{Arrow, Alchemist's Acid}</td><td style=\"text-align:center\">50 gp</td><td style=\"text-align:center\">.2 lbs</td><td style=\"text-align:left\">Explode in a @UUID[Compendium.sweb-core-rules.savage-eberron-rules.OPSttc2CAS2LC1ju.JournalEntryPage.CvRlxgap3bhXhnqA]{Small Blast Template} causing 2d4 acid damage. Half normal range.</td></tr><tr><td>@Compendium[sweb-core-rules.savage-eberron-gear.Arrow, Alchemist's Fire]{Arrow, Alchemist's Fire}</td><td style=\"text-align:center\">50 gp</td><td style=\"text-align:center\">.2 lbs</td><td style=\"text-align:left\">Explode in a @UUID[Compendium.sweb-core-rules.savage-eberron-rules.OPSttc2CAS2LC1ju.JournalEntryPage.CvRlxgap3bhXhnqA]{Small Blast Template} causing 2d4 fire damage. Half normal range.</td></tr><tr><td>@Compendium[sweb-core-rules.savage-eberron-gear.Arrow, Alchemist's Frost]{Arrow, Alchemist's Frost}</td><td style=\"text-align:center\">50 gp</td><td style=\"text-align:center\">.2 lbs</td><td style=\"text-align:left\">Explode in a @UUID[Compendium.sweb-core-rules.savage-eberron-rules.OPSttc2CAS2LC1ju.JournalEntryPage.CvRlxgap3bhXhnqA]{Small Blast Template} causing 2d4 frost damage. Half normal range.</td></tr><tr><td>@Compendium[sweb-core-rules.savage-eberron-gear.Arrow, Alchemist's Spark]{Arrow, Alchemist's Spark}</td><td style=\"text-align:center\">50 gp</td><td style=\"text-align:center\">.2 lbs</td><td style=\"text-align:left\">Explode in a @UUID[Compendium.sweb-core-rules.savage-eberron-rules.OPSttc2CAS2LC1ju.JournalEntryPage.CvRlxgap3bhXhnqA]{Small Blast Template} causing 2d4 spark damage. Half normal range.</td></tr><tr><td>@Compendium[sweb-core-rules.savage-eberron-gear.Arrow, Blunt]{Arrow, Blunt}</td><td style=\"text-align:center\">2 gp/20</td><td style=\"text-align:center\">3 lbs/20</td><td style=\"text-align:left\">Non-lethal damage. Half normal range.</td></tr><tr><td>@Compendium[sweb-core-rules.savage-eberron-gear.Arrow, Flammable]{Arrow, Flammable}</td><td style=\"text-align:center\">5 sp</td><td style=\"text-align:center\">3 lbs/20</td><td style=\"text-align:left\">Half normal range. +1d6 damage, may ignite flammable items.</td></tr><tr><td>@Compendium[sweb-core-rules.savage-eberron-gear.Arrow, Grappling]{Arrow, Grappling}</td><td style=\"text-align:center\">10 gp</td><td style=\"text-align:center\">.5 lbs</td><td style=\"text-align:left\">Half normal range.</td></tr><tr><td>@Compendium[sweb-core-rules.savage-eberron-gear.Arrow, Smoke]{Arrow, Smoke}</td><td style=\"text-align:center\">15 gp</td><td style=\"text-align:center\">.25 lbs</td><td style=\"text-align:left\">Fills a @UUID[Compendium.sweb-core-rules.savage-eberron-rules.OPSttc2CAS2LC1ju.JournalEntryPage.CvRlxgap3bhXhnqA]{Small Blast Template} with smoke. Half normal range.</td></tr><tr><td>@Compendium[sweb-core-rules.savage-eberron-gear.Arrow, Sticky]{Arrow, Sticky}</td><td style=\"text-align:center\">40 gp</td><td style=\"text-align:center\">.25 lbs</td><td style=\"text-align:left\">Alchemical arrow that <em>@Compendium[sweb-core-rules.savage-eberron-powers.Entangle]{entangles}</em> a single target. Half normal range.</td></tr><tr><td>@Compendium[sweb-core-rules.savage-eberron-gear.Arrow, Whistling]{Arrow, Whistling}</td><td style=\"text-align:center\">1 sp</td><td style=\"text-align:center\">.15 lbs</td><td style=\"text-align:left\">Emit a keening sound audible within 30\" of it's flight path.</td></tr><tr><td>@Compendium[sweb-core-rules.savage-eberron-gear.Bolt]{Bolt}</td><td style=\"text-align:center\">1 gp/10</td><td style=\"text-align:center\">1 lbs/10</td><td style=\"text-align:left\">—</td></tr><tr><td>@Compendium[sweb-core-rules.savage-eberron-gear.Bolt, Alchemist's Acid]{Bolt, Alchemist's Acid}</td><td style=\"text-align:center\">50 gp</td><td style=\"text-align:center\">.2 lbs</td><td style=\"text-align:left\">Explode in a @UUID[Compendium.sweb-core-rules.savage-eberron-rules.OPSttc2CAS2LC1ju.JournalEntryPage.CvRlxgap3bhXhnqA]{Small Blast Template} causing 2d4 acid damage. Half normal range.</td></tr><tr><td>@Compendium[sweb-core-rules.savage-eberron-gear.Bolt, Alchemist's Fire]{Bolt, Alchemist's Fire}</td><td style=\"text-align:center\">50 gp</td><td style=\"text-align:center\">.2 lbs</td><td style=\"text-align:left\">Explode in a @UUID[Compendium.sweb-core-rules.savage-eberron-rules.OPSttc2CAS2LC1ju.JournalEntryPage.CvRlxgap3bhXhnqA]{Small Blast Template} causing 2d4 fire damage. Half normal range.</td></tr><tr><td>@Compendium[sweb-core-rules.savage-eberron-gear.Bolt, Alchemist's Frost]{Bolt, Alchemist's Frost}</td><td style=\"text-align:center\">50 gp</td><td style=\"text-align:center\">.2 lbs</td><td style=\"text-align:left\">Explode in a @UUID[Compendium.sweb-core-rules.savage-eberron-rules.OPSttc2CAS2LC1ju.JournalEntryPage.CvRlxgap3bhXhnqA]{Small Blast Template} causing 2d4 frost damage. Half normal range.</td></tr><tr><td>@Compendium[sweb-core-rules.savage-eberron-gear.Bolt, Alchemist's Spark]{Bolt, Alchemist's Spark}</td><td style=\"text-align:center\">50 gp</td><td style=\"text-align:center\">.2 lbs</td><td style=\"text-align:left\">Explode in a @UUID[Compendium.sweb-core-rules.savage-eberron-rules.OPSttc2CAS2LC1ju.JournalEntryPage.CvRlxgap3bhXhnqA]{Small Blast Template} causing 2d4 spark damage. Half normal range.</td></tr><tr><td>@Compendium[sweb-core-rules.savage-eberron-gear.Bolt, Flammable]{Bolt, Flammable}</td><td style=\"text-align:center\">5 sp</td><td style=\"text-align:center\">1 lbs/10</td><td style=\"text-align:left\">Half normal range. +1d6 damage, may ignite flammable items.</td></tr><tr><td>@Compendium[sweb-core-rules.savage-eberron-gear.Bolt, Grappling]{Bolt, Grappling}</td><td style=\"text-align:center\">10 gp</td><td style=\"text-align:center\">.5 lbs</td><td style=\"text-align:left\">Half normal range.</td></tr><tr><td>@Compendium[sweb-core-rules.savage-eberron-gear.Sling Bullets]{Sling Bullets}</td><td style=\"text-align:center\">2 cp</td><td style=\"text-align:center\">.05 lbs</td><td style=\"text-align:left\">—</td></tr></tbody></table><p></p><table><tbody><tr><th class=\"main-heading\" colspan=\"7\">Siege Engines</th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"7\"><p>Catapults and trebuchets are mechanical devices that hurl large stones at enemy defenses or ranks of troops. They normally require a crew of eight to load the projectile, crank down the lever that propels it, then sight and aim it. Firing can be done by a single person (@Compendium[sweb-core-rules.savage-eberron-skills.Shooting]{Shooting}), but loading the projectile takes at least four.</p><p>A ballista is a mechanical engine designed to fire a massive crossbow bolt. One person can fire the device (@Compendium[sweb-core-rules.savage-eberron-skills.Shooting]{Shooting}). One person can reload, although it’s faster with two people.</p><p>A ram is a movable scaffold with a heavy wooden pole suspended by rope or chains. A crew of at least two is needed to swing the ram pole to batter another object. Up to eight people can swing the ram, with the leader making the attack roll (@Compendium[sweb-core-rules.savage-eberron-skills.Athletics]{Athletics}) and others providing @Compendium[sweb-core-rules.savage-eberron-rules.Support]{Support}.</p><p>A siege tower is a massive wooden tower on wheels, designed for scaling walls. Moving the structure requires at least a crew of eight, who can push the device at @UUID[Compendium.sweb-core-rules.savage-eberron-rules.1hmxcp48L0ZxhzeE.JournalEntryPage.5QA7pQEuHMHqFdoe#movement]{Pace} 1 from within the tower on the ground (double that if 16 individuals push the tower, and triple it if 24 push). Those within have complete @Compendium[sweb-core-rules.savage-eberron-rules.Cover and Obstacles]{cover} and solid wooden walls until the ramp drops, usually at the highest level. Some siege towers may have arrow slits on the higher levels as well, allowing archers to fire as they approach the enemy walls.</p></td></tr><tr><th class=\"sub-heading left\">Type</th><th class=\"sub-heading centered\">Range</th><th class=\"sub-heading centered\">Damage</th><th class=\"sub-heading centered\">AP</th><th class=\"sub-heading centered\">ROF</th><th class=\"sub-heading centered\">Blast</th><th class=\"sub-heading centered\">Cost</th></tr><tr><td>Ballista</td><td style=\"text-align:center\">15/30/60</td><td style=\"text-align:center\">3d6</td><td style=\"text-align:center\">4</td><td style=\"text-align:center\">Special</td><td style=\"text-align:center\">—</td><td style=\"text-align:center\">500 gp</td></tr><tr class=\"table-body-notes\"><td colspan=\"7\"><em><strong>Notes: </strong></em>Heavy Weapon (HW), Reload time is 5 minutes for a solo operator, or 2 minutes with a crew of 2.</td></tr><tr><td>Catapult</td><td style=\"text-align:center\">24/48/96</td><td style=\"text-align:center\">3d6</td><td style=\"text-align:center\">4</td><td style=\"text-align:center\">Special</td><td style=\"text-align:center\">MBT</td><td style=\"text-align:center\">800 gp</td></tr><tr class=\"table-body-notes\"><td colspan=\"7\"><em><strong>Notes: </strong></em>heavy Weapon (HW), Reload time is every 5 minutes with a crew of 4.</td></tr><tr><td>Ram</td><td style=\"text-align:center\">—</td><td style=\"text-align:center\">2d6</td><td style=\"text-align:center\">—</td><td style=\"text-align:center\">—</td><td style=\"text-align:center\">—</td><td style=\"text-align:center\">1,000 gp</td></tr><tr class=\"table-body-notes\"><td colspan=\"7\"><em><strong>Notes: </strong></em>Not a ranged weapon, used to batter objects. See Breaking Things.</td></tr><tr><td>Siege Tower</td><td style=\"text-align:center\">—</td><td style=\"text-align:center\">—</td><td style=\"text-align:center\">—</td><td style=\"text-align:center\">—</td><td style=\"text-align:center\">—</td><td style=\"text-align:center\">2,000 gp</td></tr><tr class=\"table-body-notes\"><td colspan=\"7\"><em><strong>Notes: </strong></em>Not a ranged weapon, used to scale walls; shooters can fire from upper floors.</td></tr><tr><td>Trebucjet</td><td style=\"text-align:center\">30/60/120</td><td style=\"text-align:center\">3d8</td><td style=\"text-align:center\">4</td><td style=\"text-align:center\">Special</td><td style=\"text-align:center\">MBT</td><td style=\"text-align:center\">1,000 gp</td></tr><tr class=\"table-body-notes\"><td colspan=\"7\"><em><strong>Notes: </strong></em>Heavy Weapon (HW), Reload time is every 5 minutes with a crew of 4.</td></tr></tbody></table></div>","markdown":""},"video":{"controls":true,"volume":0.5},"src":null,"system":{},"ownership":{"default":-1},"flags":{}},{"sort":600000,"name":"Adventuring Gear","type":"text","_id":"gqNq2iZELkeJTMgv","title":{"show":false,"level":1},"image":{},"text":{"format":1,"content":"<div class=\"sweb-core\"><h1 class=\"wide\">Adventuring Gear</h1><table><tbody><tr><th class=\"main-heading\" colspan=\"4\">Common Gear</th></tr><tr><th class=\"sub-heading left\">Items</th><th class=\"sub-heading center\">Cost</th><th class=\"sub-heading center\">Weight</th><th class=\"sub-heading center\" style=\"width:50%\">Notes</th></tr><tr><th class=\"bar-heading\" colspan=\"4\"><span class=\"no-class\">Adventuring Gear</span></th></tr><tr><td>@Compendium[sweb-core-rules.savage-eberron-gear.Backpack]{Backpack}  </td><td style=\"text-align:center\">2 gp</td><td style=\"text-align:center\">2</td><td style=\"text-align:left\">Halves the effective weight of the things inside.</td></tr><tr><td>@Compendium[sweb-core-rules.savage-eberron-gear.Ballbearings]{Ballbearings}</td><td style=\"text-align:center\">1 gp</td><td style=\"text-align:center\">1</td><td style=\"text-align:left\">One batch covers a @UUID[Compendium.sweb-core-rules.savage-eberron-rules.OPSttc2CAS2LC1ju.JournalEntryPage.CvRlxgap3bhXhnqA]{Small Blast Template}, two a @UUID[Compendium.sweb-core-rules.savage-eberron-rules.OPSttc2CAS2LC1ju.JournalEntryPage.CvRlxgap3bhXhnqA]{Medium}, and three a @UUID[Compendium.sweb-core-rules.savage-eberron-rules.OPSttc2CAS2LC1ju.JournalEntryPage.CvRlxgap3bhXhnqA]{Large}. Counts as Difficult Ground; anyone moving through the area must make an @Compendium[sweb-core-rules.savage-eberron-skills.Athletics]{Athletics} roll or stop moving for one round. A @Compendium[sweb-core-rules.savage-eberron-rules.Trait Rolls]{Critical Failure} causes the person to be knocked @Compendium[sweb-core-rules.savage-eberron-rules.Prone]{Prone}.</td></tr><tr><td>@Compendium[sweb-core-rules.savage-eberron-gear.Bedroll]{Bedroll}</td><td style=\"text-align:center\">1 gp</td><td style=\"text-align:center\">3</td><td style=\"text-align:left\">—</td></tr><tr><td>@Compendium[sweb-core-rules.savage-eberron-gear.Bell]{Bell}</td><td style=\"text-align:center\">1 gp</td><td style=\"text-align:center\">—</td><td style=\"text-align:left\">—</td></tr><tr><td>@Compendium[sweb-core-rules.savage-eberron-gear.Blanket]{Blanket}</td><td style=\"text-align:center\">5 sp</td><td style=\"text-align:center\">2</td><td style=\"text-align:left\">—</td></tr><tr><td>@Compendium[sweb-core-rules.savage-eberron-gear.Caltrops]{Ca